lastCommitMessage: Update agora_market_dart_sdk dependency reference and add Store Management features
- Updated the agora_market_dart_sdk dependency reference in pubspec.yaml and pubspec.lock to a new commit hash for consistency.
- Introduced Store Management functionality in the admin section, including navigation and UI elements for managing stores.
- Enhanced AdminDashboardPage and AdminShellPage to include Store Management options, improving overall admin navigation experience.
